{"tid":2038674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現在還鼓吹/信奉「Be water」「單獨行動」「快閃」呢套的，就是負責拘捕你那個","createTime":"2020-05-27T16:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T16:54:12.000Z","uid":230104,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d586cf21a5e19735c4c9ce4e19ad5282a811aef2","tid":2038674,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:37:06.000Z","msg":"Be water後面既階段是最反智的，一早已被臥底破左呢招<br />\n<br />\n牠們而家最想你地單獨行事， 以為be water最安全， 其實是最危險<br />\n<br />\n連登開post叫人「快閃」果批人，就係正正躲藏私家車上等捉人果批，手到拿來， 十次十次被捉既都係be water手足，有片證明<br />\n<br />\n你有6尺高+阿諾舒華辛力加既肌肉另計，如果無，請勿再小隊/離隊行街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要還是人數，要思考下點樣喺另一就近區域先聚集好一定人數先好操去目的地<br />\n<br />\n最少要聚到1000人或以上先出發，人多才好辦事，勿四散<br />\n<br />\n就算大煙都要向同一方向散，勿雞飛狗走"},{"pid":"fff41538580f3c7ec5e51ad25acf321f1e023fe5","tid":2038674,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2c4f8fa057751f8e004fa2a717bbf71b429adc4","tid":2038674,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"夫兵形象水，水之形，避高而趨下：兵之形，避實而擊虛；水因地而制流，兵因敵而制勝。故兵無常勢，水無常形；能因敵變化而取勝，謂之神。故五行無常勝，四時無常位，日有短長"},{"pid":"48801550a42c1b1e2a04fd9f99705d5221415c5f","tid":2038674,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"夫兵形象水，水之形，避高而趨下：兵之形，避實而擊虛；水因地而制流，兵因敵而制勝。故兵無常勢，水無常形；能因敵變化而取勝，謂之神。故五行無常勝，四時無常位，日有短長，月有死生。"},{"pid":"809ee49ed277e417755fdc63b9b7d05cc2426282","tid":2038674,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:49:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dda46a673ce3f0f5af64f6bb4a3d0594af1f0bf5","tid":2038674,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1007f1e1a69ade2a4d3e42f56e9b537dd660ea2","tid":2038674,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906fbc8fae015dc047ecef7b8bf9baece2e5b860","tid":2038674,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"be water 係行雲流動，唔係散水"},{"pid":"e3d467a1fcbee29336feeb7ca1055455d7bb8db1","tid":2038674,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"Be water/快閃 =落單<br />\n<br />\n邊個最想見？"},{"pid":"f4a3d335be0b701bfa73b394734622c168c1fd47","tid":2038674,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee1c162e1b0618a63a61456821a2786a3957177","tid":2038674,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"共識好緊要"},{"pid":"69d6bb60de69a05eb8e3504809fdb657d59738ea","tid":2038674,"uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5560a1984a24d95e18257a3a08972fb8a62ce15e","tid":2038674,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dd66991d1936dde00414f976b50c059a21ddb78f","tid":2038674,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:54:12.000Z","msg":"呢個真, 除非你自己plan咗目標, 熟悉地型, 單兵能力極高,<br />\n唔係嘅話, 唔該跟大隊行。"}]}